Available now on iTunes and On Demand!
Check out our story for swipe up to watch 🎥 🍿 

With actors: @elisabethrohm @codychristian @kevinpollak123 @bliv17 @jude.manley #ad #notoriousnick #notoriousnickmovie2021

Watch is NOW on iTunes, On Demand, and select theaters 🎭 

Two FBI agents cross paths with Crawford, a Florida cop who's investigating a string of murders that appear to be related. When an undercover sting goes horribly wrong, Crawford soon finds himself in a twisted game of cat and mouse with the killer.

With @meganfox @machinegunkelly @emilehirsch @reallycaitlinxox @oliveabercrombie @lukashaas

node.text:
If you were framed of killing the love of your life, what would you do?

In this modern-day Romeo and Juliet, star-crossed lovers are torn apart by cultural tensions between the East and the West. Sarah takes her American boyfriend Frank to her home country in the Arab world.

Available to watch on iTunes and On Demand! 🔥

With actors: @mickey_rourke_ @therealseanstone @lafouine78 @ericrobertsactor @officialtinylister @louismandylorofficial @tysonofficially #ad #nightwalkmovie #nightwalkmovie2021

@basharjkatou is a 7-figure Amazon seller who grew up a war refugee and now lives life on his own terms as a successful business owner.

He founded a university to show people how to make Amazon their fun side hustle and more!

Follow him to level up @basharjkatou 💪🏼

node.text:
Life is 10% what happens to me and 90% of how I react to it 💯
#MotivationMafia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How to overcome stress and anxiety: MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.

node.text: If you deal with stress and anxiety daily, here are a few things that you can do in order to relieve symptoms!

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'How to overcome stress and anxiety: MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.
Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says '1. Exercise 2. Write it out 3. Spend time with friends and family. MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.
Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says '4. Laugh 5. Learn to say no 6. Listen to calming music 7. Meditation MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.
Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'The best payback is getting yourself together and doing better! MOTIVATIONMAF'.

node.text: The biggest slap to the face is letting them see you doing better after you overcame everything that was meant to destroy you 💯

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 08, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Some ppl don't understand what you bring to the table until they see you in action at another table'.

node.text:
True or false? Comment below!
#MotivationMafia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 08, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard and text that says 'Stop telling people your business. Some people talk to you so they can talk about you MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.

node.text:
The smarter you become the less you speak 💯
#MotivationMafia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Change isn't meant to be easy. It's meant to rip up your roots and put you in new soil where your roots can deepen. It's going to be ok in the long un.'.

node.text:
When in doubt, choose change. I cannot say whether things will get better if we change; what I can say is they must change if they are to get better.
#MotivationMafia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A man with hustle needs a woman with a vision. MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.

node.text:
Do you agree? 💯
#MotivationMafia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A man with hustle needs a woman with a vision. MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.
Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 07, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'A woman with hustle needs man with amanwithavision. a vision. MOTIVATIONMAFIA'.

Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'One of the most underrated Ingredients for having a good life is a clear conscious To know you aren't out here doing people dirty, hiding who you are, or screwing people over lets you sleep peaceful at night Karma IS real, energy is contagious Live accordingly'.

node.text:
Love accordingly 💯
#MotivationMafia

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Motivation Mafia ™ on September 06, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Stop judging your craft based on how much applause it received. MOTIVATIONMA'.

node.text: Stop looking for external validation. Believe in yourself so much that it doesn’t matter who believes in your craft.
